{
  "video_id": "1tcqfWki-hw",
  "title": "A life-saving invention that prevents human stampedes | Nilay Kulkarni",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12691.0,
      "end_time": 13969.0,
      "text": "I was only nine"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13993.0,
      "end_time": 18916.0,
      "text": "when my grandfather first described to me the horrors he witnessed six years earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18940.0,
      "end_time": 21844.0,
      "text": "when human stampedes killed 39 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21868.0,
      "end_time": 23884.0,
      "text": "in our hometown of Nashik, India."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24461.0,
      "end_time": 27750.0,
      "text": "It was during the 2003 Nashik Kumbh Mela,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27774.0,
      "end_time": 30746.0,
      "text": "one of the world&#39;s largest religious gatherings."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31213.0,
      "end_time": 34943.0,
      "text": "Every 12 years, over 30 million Hindu worshippers"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34967.0,
      "end_time": 36546.0,
      "text": "descend upon our city --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36570.0,
      "end_time": 39410.0,
      "text": "which is built only for 1.5 million people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39434.0,
      "end_time": 41770.0,
      "text": "and stay for 45 days."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41601.0,
      "end_time": 44672.0,
      "text": "The main purpose is to wash away all their sins"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44696.0,
      "end_time": 47210.0,
      "text": "by bathing in the river Godavari."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47807.0,
      "end_time": 50450.0,
      "text": "And stampedes may easily happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50690.0,
      "end_time": 53346.0,
      "text": "because a high-density crowd moves at a slow pace."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54200.0,
      "end_time": 58311.0,
      "text": "Apart from Nashik, this event happens in three other places in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58335.0,
      "end_time": 60540.0,
      "text": "with varying frequency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60780.0,
      "end_time": 62847.0,
      "text": "and between 2001 and 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62871.0,
      "end_time": 68369.0,
      "text": "over 2,400 lives have been lost in stampedes at these events."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69362.0,
      "end_time": 71219.0,
      "text": "What saddened me the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71243.0,
      "end_time": 75758.0,
      "text": "is seeing people around me resigning to the city&#39;s fate"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75782.0,
      "end_time": 79607.0,
      "text": "in witnessing the seemingly inevitable deaths of dozens"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79631.0,
      "end_time": 80908.0,
      "text": "at every Kumbh Mela."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81448.0,
      "end_time": 82878.0,
      "text": "I sought to change this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82902.0,
      "end_time": 85877.0,
      "text": "and I thought, why can&#39;t I try to find a solution to this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85901.0,
      "end_time": 87389.0,
      "text": "Because I knew it is wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87701.0,
      "end_time": 91152.0,
      "text": "Having learned coding at an early age and being a maker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91177.0,
      "end_time": 92845.0,
      "text": "I considered the wild idea --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92869.0,
      "end_time": 94570.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94810.0,
      "end_time": 95466.0,
      "text": "[Makers always find a way]"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95490.0,
      "end_time": 98554.0,
      "text": "I considered the wild idea of building a system"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98579.0,
      "end_time": 101410.0,
      "text": "that would help regulate the flow of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101650.0,
      "end_time": 104540.0,
      "text": "and use it in the next Kumbh Mela in 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104780.0,
      "end_time": 107683.0,
      "text": "to have fewer stampedes and, hopefully, fewer deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108177.0,
      "end_time": 110648.0,
      "text": "It seemed like a mission impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110672.0,
      "end_time": 112440.0,
      "text": "a dream too big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112464.0,
      "end_time": 114645.0,
      "text": "especially for a 15-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114669.0,
      "end_time": 118208.0,
      "text": "yet that dream came true in 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118232.0,
      "end_time": 121925.0,
      "text": "when not only did we succeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121949.0,
      "end_time": 124901.0,
      "text": "in reducing the stampedes and their intensity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124925.0,
      "end_time": 127102.0,
      "text": "but we marked 2015"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127126.0,
      "end_time": 131133.0,
      "text": "as the first Nashik Kumbh Mela to have zero stampedes."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131596.0,
      "end_time": 136934.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136958.0,
      "end_time": 139444.0,
      "text": "It was the first time in recorded history"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139468.0,
      "end_time": 142214.0,
      "text": "that this event passed without any casualties."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142888.0,
      "end_time": 144380.0,
      "text": "How did we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144623.0,
      "end_time": 147654.0,
      "text": "It all started when I joined an innovation workshop"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147678.0,
      "end_time": 150353.0,
      "text": "by MIT Media Lab in 2014"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150378.0,
      "end_time": 152346.0,
      "text": "called the Kumbhathon"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152371.0,
      "end_time": 156775.0,
      "text": "that aimed at solving challenges faced at the grand scale of Kumbh Mela."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157784.0,
      "end_time": 162292.0,
      "text": "Now, we figured out to solve the stampede problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162316.0,
      "end_time": 164480.0,
      "text": "we wanted to know only three things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164504.0,
      "end_time": 167243.0,
      "text": "the number of people, the location,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167267.0,
      "end_time": 170726.0,
      "text": "and the rate of the flow of people per minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171241.0,
      "end_time": 175370.0,
      "text": "So we started to look for technologies that would help us get these three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176910.0,
      "end_time": 180345.0,
      "text": "Can we distribute radio-frequency tokens to identify people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180369.0,
      "end_time": 183782.0,
      "text": "We figured out that it would be too expensive and impractical"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183806.0,
      "end_time": 185742.0,
      "text": "to distribute 30 million tags."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186545.0,
      "end_time": 189926.0,
      "text": "Can you use CCTV cameras with image-processing techniques?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189950.0,
      "end_time": 191997.0,
      "text": "Again, too expensive for that scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192210.0,
      "end_time": 194899.0,
      "text": "along with the disadvantages of being non-portable"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194923.0,
      "end_time": 197741.0,
      "text": "and being completely useless in the case of rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197765.0,
      "end_time": 200147.0,
      "text": "which is a common thing to happen in Kumbh Mela."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 201120.0,
      "end_time": 203445.0,
      "text": "Can we use cell phone tower data?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 203806.0,
      "end_time": 206273.0,
      "text": "It sounds like the perfect solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206297.0,
      "end_time": 208700.0,
      "text": "but the funny part is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208940.0,
      "end_time": 210839.0,
      "text": "most of the people do not carry cell phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210863.0,
      "end_time": 212347.0,
      "text": "in events like Kumbh Mela."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212887.0,
      "end_time": 216601.0,
      "text": "Also, the data wouldn&#39;t have been granular enough for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216625.0,
      "end_time": 219780.0,
      "text": "So we wanted something that was real-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219102.0,
      "end_time": 222419.0,
      "text": "low-cost, sturdy and waterproof,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222443.0,
      "end_time": 224854.0,
      "text": "and it was easy to get the data for processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225672.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "So we built Ashioto,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 228520.0,
      "end_time": 230137.0,
      "text": "meaning \"footstep\" in Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230161.0,
      "end_time": 234346.0,
      "text": "as it consists of a portable mat which has pressure sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234370.0,
      "end_time": 236861.0,
      "text": "which can count the number of people walking on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236885.0,
      "end_time": 239316.0,
      "text": "and sends the data over the internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 239341.0,
      "end_time": 241888.0,
      "text": "to the advanced data analysis software we created."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242483.0,
      "end_time": 245771.0,
      "text": "The possible errors, like overcounting or double-stepping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245795.0,
      "end_time": 248445.0,
      "text": "were overcome using design interventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248803.0,
      "end_time": 252329.0,
      "text": "The optimum breadth of the mat was determined to be 18 inches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 252353.0,
      "end_time": 254592.0,
      "text": "after we tested many different versions"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254616.0,
      "end_time": 257203.0,
      "text": "and observed the average stride length of a person."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258111.0,
      "end_time": 261150.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, people might step over the sensor."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263612.0,
      "text": "We started with a proof of concept built in three days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263636.0,
      "end_time": 266510.0,
      "text": "made out of cardboard and aluminum foil."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266534.0,
      "end_time": 267534.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 267559.0,
      "end_time": 269933.0,
      "text": "It worked, for real."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269957.0,
      "end_time": 272647.0,
      "text": "We built another one with aluminum composite panels"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 272671.0,
      "end_time": 274308.0,
      "text": "and piezoelectric plates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274333.0,
      "end_time": 277904.0,
      "text": "which are plates that generate a small pulse of electricity under pressure."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 278959.0,
      "end_time": 282228.0,
      "text": "We tested this at 30 different pilots in public,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 282252.0,
      "end_time": 285974.0,
      "text": "in crowded restaurants, in malls, in temples, etc.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 285998.0,
      "end_time": 287632.0,
      "text": "to see how people reacted."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 288720.0,
      "end_time": 290743.0,
      "text": "And people let us run these pilots"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290767.0,
      "end_time": 297243.0,
      "text": "because they were excited to see localites work on problems for the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 297680.0,
      "end_time": 300799.0,
      "text": "I was 15 and my team members were in their early 20s."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 301736.0,
      "end_time": 306227.0,
      "text": "When the sensors were colored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306251.0,
      "end_time": 309920.0,
      "text": "people would get scared and would ask us questions like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309116.0,
      "end_time": 311323.0,
      "text": "\"Will I get electrocuted if I step on this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 311347.0,
      "end_time": 312347.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 312372.0,
      "end_time": 316744.0,
      "text": "Or, if it was very obvious that it was an electronic sensor on the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316768.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "they would just jump over it."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318285.0,
      "end_time": 319361.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319385.0,
      "end_time": 322449.0,
      "text": "So we decided to design a cover for the sensor"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322473.0,
      "end_time": 325530.0,
      "text": "so that people don&#39;t have to worry what it is on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325554.0,
      "end_time": 327530.0,
      "text": "So after some experimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 327554.0,
      "end_time": 330364.0,
      "text": "we decided to use an industrial sensor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 330388.0,
      "end_time": 333357.0,
      "text": "used as a safety trigger in hazardous areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 333381.0,
      "end_time": 334532.0,
      "text": "as the sensor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 334556.0,
      "end_time": 336637.0,
      "text": "and a black neoprene rubber sheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 336661.0,
      "end_time": 337903.0,
      "text": "as the cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338374.0,
      "end_time": 341191.0,
      "text": "Now, another added benefit of using black rubber"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 341215.0,
      "end_time": 344842.0,
      "text": "was that dust naturally accumulates over the surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 344866.0,
      "end_time": 347515.0,
      "text": "eventually camouflaging it with the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347540.0,
      "end_time": 352652.0,
      "text": "We also had to make sure that the sensor is no higher than 12 millimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353206.0,
      "end_time": 355435.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, people might trip over it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 355459.0,
      "end_time": 357364.0,
      "text": "which in itself would cause stampedes."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357792.0,
      "end_time": 361578.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 361603.0,
      "end_time": 362965.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want that."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 362989.0,
      "end_time": 364777.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 364802.0,
      "end_time": 368881.0,
      "text": "So we were able to design a sensor which was only 10 millimeters thick."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 369469.0,
      "end_time": 371709.0,
      "text": "Now the data is sent to the server in real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 371733.0,
      "end_time": 373381.0,
      "text": "and a heat map is plotted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 373405.0,
      "end_time": 376748.0,
      "text": "taking into account all the active devices on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 376772.0,
      "end_time": 381570.0,
      "text": "The authorities could be alerted if the crowd movement slowed down"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 381810.0,
      "end_time": 384216.0,
      "text": "or if the crowd density moved beyond a desired threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 384992.0,
      "end_time": 389984.0,
      "text": "We installed five of these mats in the Nashik Kumbh Mela 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 390800.0,
      "end_time": 392397.0,
      "text": "and counted over half a million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 392422.0,
      "end_time": 394104.0,
      "text": "in 18 hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394128.0,
      "end_time": 398505.0,
      "text": "ensuring that the data was available in real time at various checkpoints,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 398529.0,
      "end_time": 400405.0,
      "text": "ensuring a safe flow of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 400429.0,
      "end_time": 403873.0,
      "text": "Now, this system, eventually, with other innovations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 403898.0,
      "end_time": 407500.0,
      "text": "is what helped prevent stampedes altogether at that festival."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 407585.0,
      "end_time": 410457.0,
      "text": "The code used by Ashioto during Kumbh Mela"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 410482.0,
      "end_time": 413894.0,
      "text": "will soon be made publicly available, free to use for anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 413918.0,
      "end_time": 415895.0,
      "text": "I would be glad if someone used this code"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 415919.0,
      "end_time": 418131.0,
      "text": "to make many more gatherings safer."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 418878.0,
      "end_time": 420804.0,
      "text": "Having succeeded at Kumbh Mela"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 420828.0,
      "end_time": 424739.0,
      "text": "has inspired me to help others who may also suffer from stampedes."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 424764.0,
      "end_time": 427573.0,
      "text": "The design of the system makes it adaptable"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 427597.0,
      "end_time": 429591.0,
      "text": "to pretty much any event"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429615.0,
      "end_time": 433411.0,
      "text": "that involves an organized gathering of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 433435.0,
      "end_time": 437745.0,
      "text": "And my new dream is to improve, adapt and deploy the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 437769.0,
      "end_time": 443238.0,
      "text": "all over the world to prevent loss of life and ensure a safe flow of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 443262.0,
      "end_time": 446490.0,
      "text": "because every human soul is precious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 446730.0,
      "end_time": 448450.0,
      "text": "whether at concerts or sporting events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 448475.0,
      "end_time": 450362.0,
      "text": "the Maha Kumbh Mela in Allahabad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 450386.0,
      "end_time": 451837.0,
      "text": "the Hajj in Mecca,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 451861.0,
      "end_time": 453758.0,
      "text": "the Shia procession to Karbala"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 453782.0,
      "end_time": 455265.0,
      "text": "or at the Vatican City."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 455893.0,
      "end_time": 457770.0,
      "text": "So what do you all think, can we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 457794.0,
      "end_time": 458945.0,
      "text": "(Audience) Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 458969.0,
      "end_time": 460120.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460144.0,
      "end_time": 461145.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 461169.0,
      "end_time": 464438.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}